detail_description: Papa Gente is a seafood restaurant with excellent service and a really friendly atmosphere. The food is of the highest quality, and it's hard to get lost in the midst of all the delicious dishes on offer. There's plenty of variety on the menu, so there's definitely something for everyone to enjoy.
name: Papa Gente
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 201 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: This pizzeria is a great place for delicious pizza. The prices are reasonable, and the pizza dough is really tasty and fresh. The service can be a bit slow, but that doesn't even bother most of the customers. Some of our favourites were the Calabresa pizza with crispy bacon and the Prawn pizza with catupity sauce. Overall, this pizzeria is definitely worth checking out!
name: 7 Pizzas Praia do Forte
address: Avenue Antônio Carlos Magalhães, Praça da Música, 448, Mata de São João - BA, 42280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Sabor da Villa Restaurante do Zequinha is a top choice for those seeking high-quality home-cooked food at a great price. The restaurant offers incredible flavors and features dishes from the rich Bahian cuisine, such as the popular grilled octopus. Zequinha takes pride in serving home-style food with a mother's touch, ranging from simple rice and beans to the famous house moqueca.
name: Sabor da Vila Restaurante do Zequinha
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 159 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Xica's Bistrô, located in Beco do Arlindo, is a tranquil and harmonious establishment in Praia do Forte. Its cozy atmosphere is an added bonus for customers, as it offers high-quality typical dishes representing the cuisine of Bahia with great respect. The restaurant impeccably reproduces classic delicacies of northeastern Brazilian gastronomy.
name: Xica's Bistrô - Praia do Forte
address: R. da Aurora, 41 - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Nestled in the charming village of Praia do Forte, Souza Bar e Restaurante is a timeless classic known for serving the best fish cakes in the galaxy. The bar features solid wood tables scattered throughout a lush garden and offers a menu filled with traditional Bahian dishes like sururu broth, crab casquinha, and flavorful moquecas. Visitors can enjoy an animated musical program that heats up the late afternoon.
name: Souza Bar e Restaurante
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48287-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante Donana, a renowned establishment in Salvador, has extended its excellence to the Praia do Forte. It's the perfect spot for those seeking the best of Bahian cuisine. The shrimp stew and various moquecas are standout dishes at this restaurant. Known for serving some of the best moquecas in Salvador, Donana also offers regional delights like abara and mixed sururu and shrimp broth.
name: Restaurante Donana - Praia do Forte
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, s/n - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 40000-000, Brazil

detail_description: Vinopizza is a charming restaurant located in a quaint side street in Praia do Forte. It offers world-class cuisine within the chic setting of a fisherman's village. The establishment is highly recommended for its fantastic service, delectable food, and an impressive selection of drinks and desserts. With delicious pizza options, including many vegetarian choices, Vinopizza has garnered praise for its culinary offerings.
name: Vinopizza
address: R. da Aurora, 41 - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante LA VILLA is a romantic and tranquil dining spot with a cozy atmosphere and ambient music. Located in Vila Nova Praia on Costa do Sauipe, it offers both tasting menu and à la carte options. While the prices are considered high, the quality of food and presentation is commendable. The restaurant serves delicious drinks including caipirinhas, but the children's menu has limited choices.
name: Restaurante LA VILLA
address: Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, Brazil

detail_description: Il Cantuccio is a small, family-owned Italian restaurant that is popular for its delicious homemade pasta and mouthwatering sauces. The atmosphere is casual and the prices are very reasonable. Il Cantuccio is perfect for anyone looking for a great Italian meal at a convenient location.
name: il Cantuccio
address: Beco de Dona Nita, Travessa da Rua Principal, Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Nestled in the heart of Imbassai, Jerimum Café e Nega Fulô Pizzaria stands out as a beloved dining destination. This charming spot is renowned for its diverse menu that features mouthwatering wood-fired pizzas, generously topped to satisfy any craving. Whether you're winding down with a cozy evening meal or enjoying a delightful breakfast filled with local specialties, this café offers the perfect ambiance to savor your time in the village.
name: Jerimum Café e Nega Fulô Pizzaria
address: Alameda das Amendoeiras, s/n - Praia Imbassaí, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Nestled in a charming locale, Restaurante Taverna Paradiso stands out as a beacon of Italian cuisine, seamlessly blending rustic charm with sophisticated elegance. This establishment takes pride in its commitment to traditional Italian gastronomy, offering an array of mouthwatering dishes that are sure to tantalize your taste buds. Signature offerings like the shrimp and lemon tagliatelle and the lamb rack paired with porcini risotto showcase their culinary expertise.
name: Restaurante Taverna Paradiso
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, AV214, Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48287-000, Brazil

detail_description: Casa da Nati, located in Praia do Forte, has evolved from serving only breakfast to offering traditional meals for lunch and dinner. The restaurant is known for its generous portions at reasonable prices compared to others in the area. It also provides a children's menu and attentive service. Visitors praise the delicious and well-seasoned dishes, including options for vegetarians. While some note that the cleanliness could be improved, many appreciate the friendly staff and overall dining experience.
name: Casa da Nati
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 347 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Vânia Restaurante is a great spot in the Imbassai region known for its fantastic regional meals. If you're looking for a place to enjoy an excellent and affordable meal, this is the place to be. The restaurant offers a variety of options, including a "commercial" plate that won't cost you more than $R20 for a weekday lunch.
name: Restaurante Da Vânia
address: Alameda dos Hibiscus, 1 - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Se você está em busca de uma experiência gastronômica autêntica na Bahia, o Baêa Comida Típica Baiana é um destino imperdível. Este restaurante oferece um cardápio repleto de delícias típicas não apenas da Bahia, mas também do Nordeste como um todo.
name: Baêa Comida Típica Baiana
address: Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, Brazil

detail_description: Guaya's, a charming establishment located on the bustling main Street, offers a warm and inviting atmosphere. Inside, patrons can enjoy games of snooker and table tennis, while outside boasts picturesque views of the street and captivating rustic architecture. The delectable cuisine served is both uncomplicated yet flavorful. Moreover, this delightful eatery showcases an impressive collection of pottery artifacts throughout its premises.
name: Guaya's
address: Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante do Zoião, owned by the rare and charismatic figure of Zoião, offers top-notch dining with a fantastic atmosphere at the top. The signature dish, whole fish with plantains and shrimp prepared on the grill, has earned it the prestigious Panela de Barro award from Tv Bahia. Visitors praise the unique and delicious red fish with Banana da Terra for its freshness and healthiness. The restaurant is known for its magical ambiance, quiet surroundings, and stunning views.
name: Restaurante do Zoião
address: Rua das Dunas - Praia do Imbassai, Mata de São João - BA, 48289-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante Café Made in Bahia offers a unique dining experience on the terrace of Shopping Agua Viva, providing natural ventilation and stunning views of Praia do Forte. On weekends, guests can enjoy live music performances, usually featuring soothing vocals and acoustic guitar. The menu showcases regional cuisine prepared in the traditional artisanal style of Bahian culinary artistry. With delightful food options such as fish stews and a welcoming atmosphere, this restaurant is highly recommended for an enjoyable dining experience.
name: Restaurante Café Made in Bahia
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 371 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: When you find yourself in Praia Imbassai, make sure to stop by É Mass...a!! This charming eatery specializes in authentic Italian cuisine, offering a delightful array of classic dishes like pizza and pasta. The highlight here is undoubtedly the crispy, freshly baked pizza that comes straight from the oven—it's a must-try! With a welcoming atmosphere and friendly staff, É Mass...a!! provides an excellent dining experience where you can savor homemade pasta and other delectable options at reasonable prices.
name: É Mass...a!!
address: R. Mata, s/n - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-970, Brazil

detail_description: Las Margaritas is a cozy spot in Praia do Forte that offers a welcoming atmosphere and high-quality live music on weekends. With a capacity of 140 seats, it's the perfect place for pop and pop rock enthusiasts. The menu includes two vegetarian options that can be made vegan by removing the cheese. Guests recommend trying the tasty burrito.
name: Las Margaritas
address: Centro de, Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 147 - Vila, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante Iskindindin offers a rustic beach atmosphere with excellent food and attentive service. The owner personally shares the history of the place, adding a personal touch to the dining experience. Visitors praise the well-prepared and delicious dishes, such as the sensational plantain moqueca. The restaurant also receives accolades for its friendly staff who go out of their way to accommodate special dietary needs.
name: Restaurante Iskindindin
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 467 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Pizzeria Ristorante Passione, located in Praia do Forte, may have limited seating in the covered area during rainy days. However, visitors rave about their delicious pizzas and commendable service. The owner's hands-on approach ensures a well-run establishment. The wood oven-baked handmade dough pizzas are particularly popular, with the 6 cheese pizza being highly recommended. Some suggest that adding a removable awning for rainy days would enhance the dining experience due to limited indoor seating options.
name: Pizzeria Ristorante Passione
address: Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Pizza di Roma - Pizzaria e Restaurante is a great establishment that offers delicious food at affordable prices. The stromboli, a calzone-like Italian creation made with quality ingredients, is highly recommended. Their "Paulista" flavored pizza is also well-made and worth trying. Whether it's for lunch or dinner, the other dishes are known for their good flavors.
name: Pizza di Roma - Pizzaria e Restaurante
address: Alameda da Felicidade - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Lôro - Praia do Forte offers a delightful dining experience with its generous portions of vegan moqueca, served by a friendly and professional staff. It's definitely a place to revisit for an enjoyable meal.
name: O Lôro Praia do Forte: Barraca de Praia, Restaurante, Bar, Salvador BA
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 279 - Praça da Alegria, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Pizza Italia offers a wonderful thin-crust pizza that is expertly made, reminiscent of the pizzas found in São Paulo. It's a great place to visit with family, offering pleasant service and delicious food. Overall, it's a top choice for enjoying quality pizza.
name: Pizza Italia
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, Praça da Música, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Le Jardin is known for its great service, pleasant atmosphere, and delicious food, providing an excellent gastronomic experience. Visitors have praised the Moqueca de Camarao as the best they've had and have returned multiple times to enjoy the great food and ambiance. While some feel that the portion size could be a bit larger, overall satisfaction with the experience is high.
name: Le Jardin
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Mediterraneus is a top beach restaurant in Praia do Forte, offering delectable Bahian cuisine and an extensive wine list. The cozy atmosphere adds to the dining experience, with a good variety of dishes at reasonable prices. Visitors can enjoy well-prepared ceviche and grilled shrimp salad, both served in generous portions with delightful flavors. The restaurant also provides a welcoming space for young children and attentive service from the staff.
name: Mediterraneus
address: Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Se você é um amante de frutos do mar, não pode deixar de visitar o Benditos Frutos, um encantador restaurante que traz a atmosfera praiana para sua experiência gastronômica. Com uma decoração inspirada nas belas praias da Bahia e um ambiente acolhedor, este local é perfeito para desfrutar de pratos criativos à base de lagostas, mariscos e camarões.
name: Benditos frutos
address: BA-099 - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48282-970, Brazil

detail_description: Bela Nordestina - Praia do Forte Bahia is a highly recommended dining spot with great food and polite service. The portions are generous, so expect a satisfying meal for around $20 per person, including drinks. It's an ideal place to enjoy dinner or hang out with friends in a pleasant atmosphere. The menu offers delicious options like fish with fruit sauce, and visitors consistently praise the amazing food and top-notch service at this establishment.
name: Bela Nordestina
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 269 - Praça do Coreto, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Companhia do Forte is a popular dining spot in Praia do Forte known for its delectable pizzas and generous portions. The thin, crispy crust pizzas are filled with sensational toppings, such as the highly recommended Shrimp Special. While it's not the place for indulging in pasta, the restaurant offers an excellent selection of dishes like shrimp moqueca and filet mignon with gorgonzola sauce.
name: Companhia do Forte
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 176 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Casa de Farinha is a cooperative with a rich tradition passed down from generation to generation, operating for over 16 years in the village. Each week, a different family takes charge and offers an average of 15 flavors of sweet and savory tapiocas, puba cake (made from cassava flour in banana leaves), coconut candies, banana sweets, cassava flour, beijus, and gum biscuits.
name: Casa de Farinha
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Dining at Caranguejo Pirata Restaurante, a Brazilian eatery, proved to be an outstanding five-star encounter. The dishes served were incredibly indulgent and boasted an extraordinary blend of flavors and simplicity that defies explanation. One truly needs to partake in this culinary journey to grasp its true essence. As a gesture of goodwill, patrons are treated with a delectable coconut confection - a rarity like no other.
name: Caranguejo Pirata Restaurante
address: R. da Igreja - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48289-000, Brazil

name: Restaurante Polomar
address: 60, BA-099, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

name: Terroir do Axé
address: Loteamento Quinta do Castelo Praia do Forte, Lagoa Aroá, s/n Reserva sapiranga, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Terra Brasil Restaurante e Choperia is a popular dining spot in Praia do Forte, offering a diverse menu with a focus on seafood and traditional Bahian flavors. The restaurant stands out for its delicious risotto and attentive service. With its beachfront location, it provides a relaxed atmosphere for enjoying fresh seafood dishes.
name: Terra Brasil Restaurante e Choperia
address: Av. Antônio Carlos Magalhães, 512 - Loja 5 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-971, Brazil

detail_description: The location of Porto Forte Restaurante is highly appreciated, with a cozy atmosphere that creates a sense of comfort. Mr. Paulo's service is exceptional, displaying great hospitality. It has become a peaceful corner for many visitors. One tip would be to try the delicious fish cake, which is highly recommended by customers who have visited the restaurant. Additionally, there is always an array of tempting desserts available.
name: Porto Forte Restaurante
address: Rua Esmerindo Neto 5 Itacimirim Manguezal, Camaçari - BA, 42841-676, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante Point do Folha is a seafood restaurant located in the city of Praia do Forte, Mata de Sao Joao. The menu features grilled lobster as well as wonderful caipirinhas. The atmosphere is relaxing and the service attentive.
name: Restaurante Point do Folha
address: Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Cervejaria Port Royale is a fantastic bar located just on the edge of the bustling town center, offering both indoor and outdoor seating with plenty of space. Visitors can enjoy live music on certain nights while indulging in delicious snacks and refreshing drinks. Although some guests may have encountered less-than-friendly service from one waitress, the majority of the staff are known for their exceptional friendliness. It's definitely worth a visit for those looking to unwind with great drinks and a lively atmosphere.
name: Cervejaria Port Royale
address: Alameda dos Pescadores Lotes 1 e 2, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Sumptuori is a delightful haven for lovers of authentic Japanese cuisine, offering an extensive menu that showcases the best of traditional dishes. From fresh sushi and sashimi to crispy tempuras and flavorful seaweed, there's something to satisfy every palate. The teppanyaki tables provide a unique dining experience where guests can watch skilled chefs prepare their meals right before their eyes, adding an entertaining twist to the culinary journey.
name: Sumptuori
address: BA-099, Km 65 - s/n - Praia de Imbassaí, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Vilangelim Restaurant is a charming and well-ventilated establishment, surrounded by beautiful plants and adorned with rustic decor. The service provided is excellent and the food served is simply wonderful. Their menu offers a variety of delicious dishes, including shrimp salad, fish fillet, and filet mignon. Although some may prefer larger shrimp portions, the meticulous preparation ensures that it does not diminish the overall experience or value for money.
name: Vilangelim Restaurante
address: Km 63 da BA-099, s/n, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Tapas - Paris-Leon in Imbassai offers a menu with a variety of dishes and drinks. The relaxed atmosphere and attentive service make for an enjoyable dining experience. Customers recommend trying the French catupiry chicken crepe and potato Aioli, which are both delicious and generously portioned. The cozy ambiance, good music, and wonderful food make it a recommended spot in Imbassai.
name: Tapas - Paris-Leon
address: Praça da cultura - Imbassai, Mata de São João - BA, 48289-000, Brazil

detail_description: Sushi Nambá, located in Praia Do Forte, Bahia, offers an enjoyable culinary encounter with its impressive flaming sushi, delectable sashimi, and welcoming staff. This Japanese establishment provides a pleasant dining experience for those seeking alternative cuisine.
name: Sushi Nambá - Praia Do Forte - Bahia
address: Praça da Música, 30 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Xicabacana Restaurante is a cozy spot located in Vila da Praia do Forte, close to a Caixa Economica station. They offer homemade food at very affordable prices and accept debit and credit cards for meals. The restaurant has a family atmosphere and a varied menu. One of the highlights is the self-service option without a scale, allowing customers to choose buffet items at a fixed price.
name: Xicabacana Restaurante
address: Alameda da Lua, 338 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Agdá is a culinary haven that invites you to embark on a global gastronomic journey. Nestled within the Grand Palladium Imbassai, this spacious restaurant boasts an impressive array of international dishes, ensuring there's something for every palate. From exquisite main courses and vibrant salads to mouthwatering desserts, each meal promises a delightful experience. Breakfast at Agdá is particularly spectacular, featuring everything from fresh fruits and various egg preparations to savory meats and delectable waffles.
name: Agdá
address: BA-099, Km 65 - s/n - Imbassaí, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Rota Burger is a restaurant located in Praia do Forte that offers a selection of appetizing hamburgers. This establishment, along with Seu Pastel, provides quick dining options for those looking to satisfy their cravings quickly. The burgers served at Rota Burger are not only delicious but also come with exceptional customer service. The speed at which the food is prepared and served is unmatched in the town.
name: Rota Burger
address: Praça da Música, 30 - Loja 3 - Condomínio Porto das Baleias, Mata de São João - BA, 48287-000, Brazil

detail_description: Restaurante Do Lago Gourmet offers exquisite dishes in a very pleasant atmosphere with dedicated and cordial service. The attentive staff, especially Samana, ensures a perfect dining experience. The excellent dinner and impeccable service, particularly from the helpful waitress Carla, make it a must-visit. Overall, it's an excellent dining option that shouldn't be missed.
name: Restaurante Do Lago Gourmet
address: Unnamed Road, Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Nestled in the charming locale of Imbassai, Restaurante do Braz offers a delightful taste of Brazilian cuisine that is sure to please any palate. Guests can indulge in a variety of dishes, including the standout "picanha na banana na terra," perfect for sharing with family. The restaurant boasts a cozy atmosphere and an inviting outdoor area where visitors can enjoy live music while soaking up the beautiful riverside views.
name: Restaurante do Braz
address: Praia de, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Located in Praia do Forte, ITS ROCK&SPORT is a charming bar that offers delicious American-style pub food. The cozy spot plays classic rock and blues music, creating a welcoming atmosphere for visitors. Whether you're craving a taste of home or looking for a place to watch sports matches, this venue has got you covered. In addition to the great food, they also serve amazing drinks, making it an ideal spot to enjoy the night with family and friends.
name: ITS ROCK&SPORT
address: Av. do Farol, 263 - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

name: Restaurante Canteiro do Mar
address: Praca Artistas, s/n - Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, 48280-000, Brazil

detail_description: Barraca Porto da Jangada, also known as Zemar e Trudy, is a beachside bar that rivals expensive Michelin-starred restaurants with its outstanding cuisine. While the presentation may be rustic, the octopus served here is exceptionally tender and practically melts in the mouth. The staff is equally pleasant and welcoming, providing a friendly atmosphere without expectation of Michelin-star service. Considered a hidden gem, this place offers top-quality food that truly represents the local flavors.
name: Barraca Porto da Jangada (Zemar e Trudy)
address: Açu da Torre, Mata de São João - BA, Brazil
